92,"uid":171310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"將任何野都物化真係反人類"},{"pid":"b0026614fdf48d64d51cd86c6fcb325a737015e3","tid":2291592,"uid":32221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"當年大航海真係好撚高質"},{"pid":"e602fe9661d27ba85270d04691b88d7bbe734697","tid":2291592,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"371768ceae067f0a9c14b0cb6ad7c023c728ac8b","tid":2291592,"uid":26283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bffaa72ebe4f26511f74c0f80659e39235b7d96e","tid":2291592,"uid":144024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf52bab73ded9667767b0af3e9216ab703eb01df","tid":2291592,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"賣皮膚賣裝飾我唔反對但賣影響遊戲體驗嘅裝備就可以棄game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:26:03.000Z","msg":"你棄硬都得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T11:46:21.000Z","msg":"都唔知邊個諗出來<br />\n隻game同DLC一齊出<br />\n但夠膽拆幾關出去就收多你一份<br />\n<br />\nDLC你本傳整到P5咁 <br />\n一周目就過百個鐘 仲有幾個結局<br />\n我都唔介意買DLC支持下<br />\n<br />\n仆街個pokemon 劍盾 <br />\n本傳推個未完成品出嚟<br />\n一周目十幾個鐘就完 <br />\n個地圖解謎全部remove 曬<br />\n仲夠膽拆多二個DLC 叫人等年幾<br />\n但加埋都無40個鐘好意思叫RPG?<br />\n就得返加個西窿比人刷個體刷閃加耐玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗返細個玩綠寶石有對戰開拓<br />\n金銀有二個地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"Steam game DLC加加埋埋貴過主game <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a390ed306c7e6d1d056ae1b4eec9afbbb849c3b","tid":2291592,"uid":112081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:39:42.000Z","msg":"作者唔識大航海時代online?單機game來講，個系統同埋劇情真係唔錯，特別係荷蘭主線反抗西班牙嗰個劇情寫得幾好"}]}